angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79190d59131b025673c3ef352a53717cce625a4","tid":638150,"uid":54264,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/180137_09862af116b9d1b8a461773b1b0c3036.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F180137_09862af116b9d1b8a461773b1b0c3036.png&h=aeeda3d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"523d6ccbb3bbac43cd303c6832918f8750bd0219","tid":638150,"uid":23861,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"佔中是中共煽動香港人"},{"pid":"8239e158226ed2ab6911db6631adede3ec6a746d","tid":638150,"uid":25858,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"平時抵制！而家驚到頼屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e3c88cf2e74a9bda096522a411e0a41c96969e","tid":638150,"uid":6752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"抵制=開宗明義搶佢d貨,好彩既仲可以唔畀錢,打爛人地鋪頭d野<br />\n屋企夠貨食既仲洗乜買國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搶既規模愈大,內銷就仲難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1f39660efb6806af1c73c901bfcece9829c9c","tid":638150,"uid":54264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8239e158226ed2ab6911db6631adede3ec6a746d","tid":638150,"uid":25858,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"平時抵制！而家驚到頼屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"唔好激嬲侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a183ed946fe18593366ca5a997b88307e458295a","tid":638150,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece1f39660efb6806af1c73c901bfcece9829c9c","tid":638150,"uid":5426